data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite home that epitomizes rustic charm, providing a peaceful living experience. Ideally situated in a prime location near Niceville, Eglin, Hurlburt, Duke Field, 7/SFG, Destin/FWB Airport, Shalimar, and major highways, this spacious property offers convenience and accessibility. This 4-bedroom, 3-bath house spans over 2,200 square feet, resting on a comfortable .35-acre lot that offers ample yard space, perfect for adding a pool or additional storage sheds if desired. For those seeking extra storage solutions, a concrete pad is available in the backyard, ideal for an outdoor shed. Furthermore, a workshop attached to the house, just off from the newly installed wood deck, provides a versatile space for hobbies or projects.

This home has undergone significant upgrades to enhance its appeal. A total re-wire was completed before the current sellers moved in, ensuring a modern and safe electrical system. In 2021, a brand new roof, water heater, and HVAC were installed, further adding to the home's value and functionality. The entire flooring has been replaced, as well freshly painted throughout to truly modernize from floor to ceiling.

The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting double ovens that provide ample cooking space and flexibility. The heart of the home, the Great Room, captivates with its natural wood-burning fireplace and built-in shelving, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation.

Give us a call to schedule an exclusive viewing and seize the opportunity of becoming the proud owner of one of the few available properties in the highly sought-after area of Valparaiso.
